---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-sage-100 bg-cream-100">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 px-6 py-12 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Plate Notes</p>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
        Honest meal plans, real ingredients, and recipes that fit a normal weeknight.
      </p>
    </div>
    <nav aria-label="Footer">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sage-700">Explore</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/plan" class="text-ink-soft hover:text-sage-700 transition-colors">This week's plan</a></li>
        <li><a href="/recipes" class="text-ink-soft hover:text-sage-700 transition-colors">Recipe library</a></li>
        <li><a href="/shopping-list" class="text-ink-soft hover:text-sage-700 transition-colors">Shopping list</a></li>
        <li><a href="/pricing" class="text-ink-soft hover:text-sage-700 transition-colors">Pricing</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="text-ink-soft hover:text-sage-700 transition-colors">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/accessibility" class="text-ink-soft hover:text-sage-700 transition-colors">Accessibility</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sage-700">Contact</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-soft">
        Questions, feedback, or recipe requests:
        <br/>
        <a href="mailto:hello@platenotes.dcrader.dev" class="underline decoration-sage-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-sage-700">hello@platenotes.dcrader.dev</a>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-muted">
        Accessibility:
        <a href="mailto:accessibility@platenotes.dcrader.dev" class="underline decoration-sage-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-sage-700">accessibility@platenotes.dcrader.dev</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-sage-200/60">
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-5 text-xs text-ink-muted">
      &copy; {year} Plate Notes. Built by <a href="https://dcrader.dev" class="underline decoration-sage-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-sage-700">Donovan Crader &middot; dcrader.dev</a>. Recipes are for informational purposes and are not medical advice.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
